. * --- 2. Tune the discovery: specific vs broad ------------------------------
> --
. * `pyoptions("specificity=...")` controls how granular the themes are.
. * "broad" (default) gives general themes; "specific" gives finer-grained ones
> .
. di _n "{hline 60}"

